{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-066__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-001", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-066", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-066__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "老子 66.1", "sort_key": "066.001", "text_original": "江海所以能為百谷王者，以其善下之，故能為百谷王。", "text_normalized": "江海所以能為百谷王者，以其善下之，故能為百谷王。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-066__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-002", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-066", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-066__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "老子 66.2", "sort_key": "066.002", "text_original": "是以欲上民，必以言下之。", "text_normalized": "是以欲上民，必以言下之。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-066__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-003", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-066", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-066__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "老子 66.3", "sort_key": "066.003", "text_original": "欲先民，必以身後之。", "text_normalized": "欲先民，必以身後之。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-066__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-004", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-066", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-066__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "老子 66.4", "sort_key": "066.004", "text_original": "是以聖人處上而民不重，處前而民不害。", "text_normalized": "是以聖人處上而民不重，處前而民不害。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-066__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-005", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-066", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-066__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "老子 66.5", "sort_key": "066.005", "text_original": "是以天下樂推而不厭，以其不爭，故天下莫能與之爭。", "text_normalized": "是以天下樂推而不厭，以其不爭，故天下莫能與之爭。", "notes": ""}
